<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4723151>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Heteragrion gorbi. Habitus (a) and head (b) of the holotype; lateral view of left cerci of paratype (c); lateral (d) and dorsal view (e) of holotype cerci; dorsal view of left cerci of paratype (f); ventral view of cerci of holotype (g)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4723151/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4723153>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Heteragrion gorbi. Lateral view of holotype thorax (a); dorsal view of paratype thorax and prothorax (b) and wings (c)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4723153/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4723161>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Heteragrion gorbi. Paratype (a) collected in copula with a female (b)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4723161/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4723165>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Dorso-lateral view of left cerci of Heteragrion gorbi (a) and Heteragrion denisye (b)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4723165/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4723155>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Heteragrion gorbi. Female habitus (a); head (b); lateral (c), dorsal (d) and ventral (e) of genital valves." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4723155/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4723159>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Heteragrion gorbi. Lateral view of female thorax (a); dorsal view of female thorax and prothorax (b); female wings (c)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4723159/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4723163>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Habitat of Heteragrion gorbi in São Carlos, Brazil." ;
